HEADWORD: Trammeler
<hw>Tram"mel*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>trammeller</asp>.]</altsp> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who uses a trammel
net.</def> <rj><au>Nares.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who, or that which, trammels or
restrains.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trammel wheel</ent>⟦br⟧
